{
  "stem": "14156.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [CHUCKLES] people used to, you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] go and-- and exchange it for something else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I'll give you a piece of-- I give you [NON-ENGLISH], a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You got me-- give me a cigarette, or give me this, or give me that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've seen that people-- what I have-- I have never forgotten one man who came there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was from Berlin, a Jewish fellow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Little guy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One time in the morning, I seen him giving away his ration, his food ration.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First food ration in the morning, away for a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But after three, four weeks, he was skinny.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just bones.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he-- later, he ended up in the chimney.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Another thing I haven't forgotten, there was a fellow, his name was Stein.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Paul Stein.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He came with us in the same barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Paul Stein was one of our madrichim, our leaders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "From the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one night, you heard shots and somebody scream, down!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Down!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Go down!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Lay on the floor!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's what the-- the guards who were all Ukrainians, Ukrainians in SS uniform-- they ran away from Stalin, and the SS took them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They-- they weren't-- they were not good enough to put them to the front, naturally.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They probably wouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When the Russians would have seen them, they'll kill them right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Paul Stein was the first one who committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- in the morning, I got out, and I see him laying in the-- in the-- next to the-- to the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- no.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], how would I call that-- the electric-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] oh, the electric-- The fence?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fence.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There you go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The electric fence.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
